hero.title: Why unit test culture is broken
hero.excerpt: Write unit test should be as fun as writing your feature code, no matter which language you're using, it's all code at the end of the day.

stories.title: How to integrate container security scan with AWS Elastic Search and Kibana
stories.excerpt: The idea of this project is to put together all resources needed to create a Elastic Search cluster with Kibana as visualition tool.  Which will ingest data reports from Aqua Security kube-bench a Container Security monitor..
